Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:01.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}誰も知らない世界の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:06.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}止まない雨に打たれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:12.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}守りたいものを守れる強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:17.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}それを信じられなくなるひ弱さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:22.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}すべてを受け入れて　明日を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:25.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Brave Shine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:31.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}手を伸ばせばnow you see the light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}傷だらけにnow you see my light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.05,0:01:40.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}翳した刃の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:42.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}思いを重ねた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:50.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}祈りは時を超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:56.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Your brave shine
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== MAIN ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,从正面进去不太方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 从那边进去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的 刚才的都是宝具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞什么啊 强的离谱耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,相比起来 这边是中看不中用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说只有块头大…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,想要命就躲一边去 小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要搞笑还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是切还是烧都不会倒下的英雄见多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到真有男人会死而复生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是把你的人生 逸闻升华为宝具的产物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,只有那个宝具我手里没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样对本王也有点不利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但对那个男人似乎只有最上级的武具才能奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,传说 赫拉克勒斯闯过了十二道难关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,最终被迎上了神坛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,正是不屈不挠 人类忍耐的极限呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我的宝物库正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是无限暴政的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所见 杀英雄的武器应有尽有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,照顾孩子就到此为止了 赫拉克勒斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不认真起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你的试炼会全部用尽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker谁都不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是全世界最厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 切…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你的母亲被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,被最爱的男人亲手杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈说会成为圣杯 由切嗣守护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,被背叛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你 我们 都被那个男人背叛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,像道具一样 被抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人 骗人 你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事肯定都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 一个人也能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 一个人也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人似乎死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,叛徒似乎死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没有来接我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,最后也是自顾自的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,和我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我已经决定一个人活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人有家人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,除我以外的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,家人… 我的弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,对 肯定能互相厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就能互相厮杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大圣杯的火还没有熄灭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不完全的结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,战争很快就会再次开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待啊 伊莉雅斯菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,像那个人类一样 能找到生存的理由了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么每天身体都要被打开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,圣杯战争什么的 停止不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没法停止 因为那是我们的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,千年前发生的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为了再现它 我们被造了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法？ 人类的救赎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那样能获得幸福的只有人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是为什么活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有幸福的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是被使用的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就连那个阿哈特翁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,应该也没有开心过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 大家都只是启动圣杯的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为此痛苦了上千年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 你终于到达了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,到达了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你是爱因兹贝伦的到达点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的技术的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,无论今后花多少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,都做不出比你更好的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果你败了 大家都会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,阿哈特翁会自己切断电源吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为已经得出结论了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经过时了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都会放弃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,自己去死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 名为爱因兹贝伦的工场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,会停止持续千年的钻研
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然做了很多努力 但没有任何价值 这样自嘲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这太奇怪了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大家不是都活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么非要去死？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要死的只有去战斗的我一个人吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不要伤心 温柔的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就算没有价值也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然没有救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们终于能从这个债务中解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,任务 任务 任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就知道任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么爱因兹贝伦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是完全没有什么自我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我是从今天起负责照顾大小姐的塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是负责护卫的莉兹丽特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,莉兹丽特的调整还没有完成…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,招呼什么的无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你们也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 Servant呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是 召唤已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,希腊神话中大名鼎鼎的大英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,赫拉克勒斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,多么神威凛凛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,开心吧 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,既然召唤出了这样的英灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,胜利就是囊中之物了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然力量微薄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们也会赌上性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Servant什么的只是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,内心什么的无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我一个人能行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人就能赢得圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker需要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅 保护
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,少让我笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Servant什么的只是被规则束缚的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没有令咒马上就会背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经谁都不会相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,开始和Berserker的同调
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对于七成身体都由魔术回路构成的大小姐来说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Servant的回馈不是平常的Master可比
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还请小心注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅 疼就马上停止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,给我好好动起来 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你这也算最强英灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,大小姐 请切断同调
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,正式契约就留待来日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这种程度不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就能习惯驾驭 闭嘴看着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会输 因为我是全世界最厉害的Master
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,// ==================== BD EXCLUSIVE ====================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== BD EXCLUSIVE ==================== //
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 还在最终试验途中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,能活着回到城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我就能去冬木来着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 我把Berserker扔下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,反正也无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,回城里召唤新的Servant就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,下次要不疼的 不吓人的… Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 我明明抛弃你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行让我痛苦 不想让我受伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,动手 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是因为有命令 身为Servant才守护我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是以自己的意志守护了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker好强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker才不会输给那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为Berserker比谁都强！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,无论发生什么 绝对不准出手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的我们没有战斗的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 要救人 得先救了自己再去考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你的败北已经注定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何都要死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,最后放下行李如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,无牵无挂的你 还有结果本王的可能哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那就和主子一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要输
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 就给你最大的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就十一了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,终于没有退路了呢 赫拉克勒斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要是一上来就抛弃主人 还能有点胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,终究不过是狗畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只会战斗的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,同为半神本来还有点期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到居然如此愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快回来 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 叫你回到我体内的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:18:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的 人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,天之锁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦被这个锁住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是神也没法挣脱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不 像这个男人这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,神性越高越会成为它的牺牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,通过令咒的空间转移什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,本王怎么会允许
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 好疼 好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一片漆黑 什么都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要一直在那里哦 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,令人吃惊的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,最后的最后超越了自己的神话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你丫的快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就算再黑  也不怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为Berserker好强的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只要这样 我就能安心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 一直有他守护着我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然长相可怕 但真的好温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:22:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大大的块头 像爸爸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我想抱他一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有点 冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,背叛让我不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.27,0:23:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Caster想必也会头疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.40,0:23:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经坏的够彻底了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.53,0:23:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有战斗的意志 但完全不够看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.11,0:24:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不爽有你丫这种Servant存在！
